title: TESOLLO uses own actuator in DG-5F-S humanoid robotic hand
description:
TESOLLO said the technology it developed in house enables a smaller and lighter 20-DoF robot hand.

The post TESOLLO uses own actuator in DG-5F-S humanoid robotic hand appeared first on The Robot Report.
